{"tid":765591,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[AGREE?] 搭因航最大既好處 就係可以避免接觸班港喱大種乞衣","createTime":"2018-08-03T02:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T15:30:01.000Z","uid":43983,"like":226,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"284a9ebb642398f909e15c85e127fb378c77dc40","tid":765591,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"之前唔識諗為左慳果千零蚊試左人生第一次UO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你老母成班生番一聽到可以boarding就即刻衝去排隊，然後狗沖上機放handcarry<br />\n估唔到香港人真係可以一箱一箱手信咁買返黎，但係連果少少寄倉錢都出唔起，<br />\n到最後所有人上哂機，都仲有條撚樣塞住係個走廊放行李放成幾分鐘<br />\n空姐叫佢比人行先都仲可以惡返人轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係唔明呢班有錢買咁多手信，但冇錢寄倉既大種乞衣係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未計廉航DELAY、又迫又嘈等問題<br />\n<br />\n黎緊下個月去東京都係搭返因航算<br />\n起碼搭左咁多次都未見過有以上問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d91ffe63305f7eb15fbfd6d843be3d9d57c53a1","tid":765591,"uid":2679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"人地覺得慳左果啲錢先叫識諗掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a97ab17db72d3aa74235973ce1b93962119d93","tid":765591,"uid":71748,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:13:38.000Z","msg":"因航咪一樣大比乞食R upgrade"},{"pid":"77c07258bee683baeadde90a7df71746786668eb","tid":765591,"uid":43983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d91ffe63305f7eb15fbfd6d843be3d9d57c53a1","tid":765591,"uid":2679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"人地覺得慳左果啲錢先叫識諗掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"而家換里數都半年一張CV東京了，其實錢都可以慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e50a7f08322f65b18809d3fe78c892fc67926ee","tid":765591,"uid":141500,"like":50,"dislike":0